[{"Id": 1013077, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Ziyarat of Ummul Baneen (s), Mother of Hazrat Abbas (a). The name of Ummul Baneen is Fatema, the daughter of Hezaam. She was an extremely righteous, valiant, religious, accomplished and sincere lady. After the martyrdom of Hazrat Fatema Zahra (s), she became the wife of Hazrat Ali (a). She gave birth to 4 sons Abbas, Abdullah, Jafar and Usmaan. All of them fought on the side of Imam Husain (a) and achieved martyrdom. Ummul Baneen used to mourn on her 4 sons and other martyrs of Karbala. She also composed Marsiyas (Poems of sorrow) in their honour and thus she was the one who has kept the memory of Karbala alive. Recite the Ziyarat of Ummul Baneen (s) as follows…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Ummul Baneen (s) ki ziyarat jo Hazrat Abbas (a) ki waaleda hai. Dar haqeeqat Ummul Baneen ka naam Fatema binte Hezaam hai. Woh ek behtareen muttaqi aur parhez-gaar bibi thi. Hazrat Fatima Zahra (s) ki shahadat ke baad, Ummul Baneen, Hazrat Ali (a) ki biwi bani. Unse 4 awlaad huwi, Abbas, Abdullah, Jafar aur Usmaan. Inki sabhi aulaado’n ne Imam Husain (a) ki nusrat karte huwe Karbala mein shaheed huwe. Unho ne Karbala par marsiya bhi likkha aur is tarah unho ne Karbala ki yaad ko zindah rakkha. Ummul Baneen (s) ki ziyarat is tarah se hai…", "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBl