u) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010122, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be on you, the pure purified, Peace be on you, O the Patient & Thankful. Peace be on you O the Knowledgeable & who acted on the knowledge. Peace be on you O Honored (Fazila) & Purified (Zakiya). Peace be upon you O Pious (Taqiya) & Naqia. Peace be upon you O Razia & Marziya (Pleased with HIS decree). Peace be upon you the wife of the Viceregent of Allah. Peace be upon you o companion of Ameer ul Momineen. Peace be on you, O Ummul Baneen. Peace be on you, the mother of Abbas, son of Amir al-Mu’mineen, Ali ibn Abu Talib. Peace be upon you & your four sons who sacrificed their lives on Imam Hussain (as) on the day of Ashura. May Allah be pleased with you and make Heaven your home and resting place, with God’s mercy and blessings. O intimate of Allah, stand by us when Allah sits in judgment over us.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKE AYYA-TO-HAT TAIYYE-BA-TUT TAAHE-RA-TO. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKE AYYA-TO-HAS SAABE-RA-TUSH SHAAKE-RA-TO. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKE AYYA-TO-HAL AA’ME-LATO. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKE AYYA-TO-HAL FAAZE-LA-TUZ ZAKIYYA-TO. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKE AYYA-TO-HAT TAQIYYA-TUN NAQIYYA-TO. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKE AYYA-TO-HAR RAZIYYA-TUL MARZIYYA-TO. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKE YAA ZAWJA-TA WALIYYIL LAAHE. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKE YAA HA-LEELA-TA AMEERIL MO-MENEENA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKE YAA UMMAL BANEENA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKE YAA UMMUL A’BBAA-SIB-NE AMEERIL MO-MENEENA A’LAI-HIS SALAAMO. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKE WA A’LAA AW-LAADE-KIL ARBA-A’TIL MUS-TASHHE-DEENA BAIYNA YA-DAL IMAAMIL HUSAINE A’LAI-HIS SALAAMO YAWMA AA’SHOO-RAAA-E. RIZWAA-NUL LAAHE TA-AA’LAA A’LAIKE, WAJA-A’LAL LAAHO A-AA’LE-YAL JANNATE MANZE-LA-KE WA MAAWA-KE. YAA WAJEE-HATAN I’NDAL LAAHE ISHFA-EE’ LANAA I’NDAL LAAHE WA SALLAL LAAHO A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE-HIT TAIYYE-BEE-NAT TAAHE-REENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكِ اَيَّتُهَا الطَّيِّبَةُ الطَّاهِرَةُ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكِ اَيَّتُهَا الصَّابِرَةُ الشَّاكِرَةُ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكِ اَيَّتُهَا الْعَالِمَةُ الْعَامِلَةُ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكِ اَيَّتُهَا الْفَاضِلَةُ الزَّكِيَّةُ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكِ اَيَّتُهَا التَّقِيَّةُ النَّقِيَّةُ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكِ اَيَّتُهَا الرَّضِيَّةُ الْمَرْضِيَّةُ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكِ يَازَوْجَةَ وَلِيِّ اللهِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكِ يَاحَلِيْلَةَ اَمِيْرِ الْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ۔  اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكِ يَااُمَّ الْبَنِيْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكِ يَااُمَّ الْعَبَّاسِّ بْنِ اَمِيْرِ الْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ عَلَيْهِ السَّلَامُ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكِ وَعَلٰى اَوْلَادِكِ الْاَرْبَعَةِ الْمُسْتَشْهِدِيْنَ بَيْنَ يَدَيْ الْاِمَامِ الْحُسَيْنِ عَلَيْهِ السَّلَامُ يَوْمَ عَاشُوْرَآء۔ رِضْوَانُ اللهِ تَعَالٰى عَلَيْكِ ، وَجَعَلَ اللهُ اَعَالِيَ الْجَنَّةِ مَنْزِلَكِ وَمَأوَاكِ۔ يَاوَجِيْهَةً عِنْدَ اللهِ اِشْفَعِيْ لَنَا عِنْدَ اللهِ وَصَلَّى اللهُ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وّآلِهِ الطَّيِّبِيْنَ الطَّاهِرِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicTex